ComicInfo.Summary:
CROSSOVER PART 3 The Fantastic Four must join forces with one of their world’s greatest villains to survive an epic battle on an alternate Earth against the Marvel Zombies!
On an world they never thought they’d visit, the fledgling F.F. find themselves hunted by the strangest enemies imaginable.
And only one man can offer them salvation—the mutant master of magnetism—Magneto!
The story you never thought you’d see comes to its shocking end!
